reviews.review_text: Charlie, Scott, Rob & Matt ~ Remastering Masters Charlie My Brother, Scott, Rob And The Ever Present "Matthew Vernon" ....... What Can We Say, A Couple months back . On this forum I made a Request & a couple suggestions. Since then, they have all appeared on IA From This Intrepid group of Music affociendos. (-2 Sp) This show appeared awhile back remastered an shining thru like never before. Now this. A Recut Jewel. Exposing all the facets hidden by dust, friction & TIME. A Fantastic improvement in seperation. This Gem of a show Radiating from every Instrument and voice shows what can be done with the right people, the right equipment and most of all the Loving Care required to do any task well. My Compliments Guys. This Is INCREDIBLE. Go Back and listen to previous uploads if'n ya don't take my ear to heart. This iz De Snizzle. Thank You From the Bottom depths of This Grateful Soul.
